    {
      "bookmarkId": "855754_52_1213-1242",
      "chapterUid": 52,
      "range": "1213-1242",
      "markText": "“我要以自己的头脑作武器，在这艰难的尘世中闯出一条路来。”",
      "totalCount": 3996,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=855754&chapterUid=52&rangeStart=1213&rangeEnd=1242",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8b5325005d0eca8b53fcf90?chapterUid=52&rangeStart=1213&rangeEnd=1242"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "855754_61_5787-5886",
      "chapterUid": 61,
      "range": "5787-5886",
      "markText": "你有很多天赋和优点，但不必摆出来展览，因为自大会把最优秀的天才毁掉。真正的才华或品行不怕被人长期忽视；即使真的无人看到，只要你知道自己拥有它，并妥善使用它，你就会感到心满意足。谦虚才能使人充满魅力。",
      "totalCount": 3840,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=855754&chapterUid=61&rangeStart=5787&rangeEnd=5886",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8b5325005d0eca8b53fcf90?chapterUid=61&rangeStart=5787&rangeEnd=5886"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "855754_87_11419-11476",
      "chapterUid": 87,
      "range": "11419-11476",
      "markText": "劳里向她道别时，意味深长地低声说：“这一点儿用也没有，乔。我的眼睛会一直盯着你。别胡来，不然，我就去把你接回家。”",
      "totalCount": 3530,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=855754&chapterUid=87&rangeStart=11419&rangeEnd=11476",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8b5325005d0eca8b53fcf90?chapterUid=87&rangeStart=11419&rangeEnd=11476"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "855754_58_9777-9807",
      "chapterUid": 58,
      "range": "9777-9807",
      "markText": "当你们感到不满足时，想想自己所拥有的东西，并为此而心存感激。",
      "totalCount": 3196,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=855754&chapterUid=58&rangeStart=9777&rangeEnd=9807",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8b5325005d0eca8b53fcf90?chapterUid=58&rangeStart=9777&rangeEnd=9807"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "855754_56_1315-1382",
      "chapterUid": 56,
      "range": "1315-1382",
      "markText": "接下来除了轻轻的翻书声外，屋里一片宁静。这时，冬日的阳光悄悄潜入屋内，轻柔地抚摸着她们亮丽的头发和严肃的脸庞，向她们致以圣诞节的问候。",
      "totalCount": 2890,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=855754&chapterUid=56&rangeStart=1315&rangeEnd=1382",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8b5325005d0eca8b53fcf90?chapterUid=56&rangeStart=1315&rangeEnd=1382"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "855754_55_3071-3143",
      "chapterUid": 55,
      "range": "3071-3143",
      "markText": "我恨我得长大，得做马奇小姐。我恨穿长礼服，恨故作正经的漂亮小姐。我喜欢男孩子的游戏、男孩子的活儿以及男孩子风度，却偏偏是个女孩子，真是倒霉透了。",
      "totalCount": 2736,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=855754&chapterUid=55&rangeStart=3071&rangeEnd=3143",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8b5325005d0eca8b53fcf90?chapterUid=55&rangeStart=3071&rangeEnd=3143"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "855754_93_11714-11774",
      "chapterUid": 93,
      "range": "11714-11774",
      "markText": "她们就像梅格那样，认识到妇人最幸福的王国是家庭，而作为她们统治艺术最高荣耀的不是做一个女王，而是做一个聪明的妻子和母亲。",
      "totalCount": 2700,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=855754&chapterUid=93&rangeStart=11714&rangeEnd=11774",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8b5325005d0eca8b53fcf90?chapterUid=93&rangeStart=11714&rangeEnd=11774"
    },
    {
