      "chapterUid": 55,
      "range": "10283-10346",
      "markText": "把长长的缝口分为四段，分别称为欧洲、亚洲、非洲和美洲。这样果然缝得快多了。她们一边缝一边谈论针线穿越的不同国家，更觉进展神速。",
      "totalCount": 2592,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=855754&chapterUid=55&rangeStart=10283&rangeEnd=10346",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8b5325005d0eca8b53fcf90?chapterUid=55&rangeStart=10283&rangeEnd=10346"
