      "chapterUid": 58,
      "range": "3496-3532",
      "markText": "“我们不能为钱财而放弃女儿。不论贫富，我们都要厮守一起，共享天伦之乐。”",
      "totalCount": 1989,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=855754&chapterUid=58&rangeStart=3496&rangeEnd=3532",
